mp</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>704</BitOffs></SubItem><FbInfo /><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name Decoration="1007775B">CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC.CTRL_PWM</Name><BitSize>1024</BitSize><SubItem><Name>CI</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>MAN_IN</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>MANUAL</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>F</Name><Type>REAL</Type><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>Q</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>192</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Output</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>PW</Name><Type Decoration="10075153">CPNTeck_OSCAT_BASIC.PWM_DC</Type><BitSize>768</BitSize><BitOffs>256</BitOffs></SubItem><FbInfo /><Properties><Property><Name>PouType</Name><Value>FunctionBlock</Value></Property></Properties></DataType><DataType><Name Decoration="102E3915">FB_HeadboxLipsPWMControl</Name><Comment><![CDATA[
    FB_HeadboxLipsPWMControl
    Purpose:
      - Control headbox lips opening using ON/OFF modulation (PWM), no analog speed output.
      - Manual: open/close while buttons are pressed (jog).
      - Automatic: operator types a target opening [mm] and presses "adjust"; the FB drives
        the lips toward the target using PWM duty proportional to position error magnitude.
      - If manualOpenCmd or manualCloseCmd is pressed during automatic positioning, the FB
        immediately returns to manual mode.

    Features:
      - Position units in millimeters (mm).
      - Limit sensors (limitMaxSensor / limitMinSensor) inhibit motion.
      - PWM duty [%] from |positionError| with clamps (min/max duty).
      - Minimum ON time per direction (minOnTime) to protect contactors.
      - Stall detection and travel timeout.
      - Exclusive actuation (never open & close simultaneously).
      - Human-readable deviceState.

    Notes:
      - Single PWM generator; direction is applied by gating its pulse.
      - Target is clamped to [posMin_mm .. posMax_mm].
]]></Comment><BitSize>3648</BitSize><SubItem><Name>positionFeedback_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Actual opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>64</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>posMin_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Minimum allowed opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>96</BitOffs><Default><Value>0</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>posMax_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Maximum allowed opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSize>32</BitSize><BitOffs>128</BitOffs><Default><Value>25</Value></Default><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>limitMaxSensor</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE when fully open (max) limit is active]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>160</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>limitMinSensor</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ TRUE when fully closed (min) limit is active]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>168</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>manualOpenCmd</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Jog open while pressed]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>176</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>manualCloseCmd</Name><Type>BOOL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Jog close while pressed]]></Comment><BitSize>8</BitSize><BitOffs>184</BitOffs><Properties><Property><Name>ItemType</Name><Value>Input</Value></Property></Properties></SubItem><SubItem><Name>autoTargetInput_mm</Name><Type>REAL</Type><Comment><![CDATA[ Operator desired opening [mm]]]></Comment><BitSi