    FB_PressureControl_V1
    - Start pulse toggles run; Stop pulse/level forces stop
    - statusCode : INT (0=Idle, 1=Running, 2=Fault)
    - PID (OSCAT CTRL_PID) with optional reverse action
    - Input PT1 filter (OSCAT FT_PT1)
    - Engineering↔% scaling helper
