    FB_ProcessControler
    Purpose: Generic process controller with start/stop latch, status codes,
             PID (OSCAT CTRL_PID), optional reverse action, PV PT1 filter,
             engineering↔% scaling, drive run supervision, and HMI displays.

    Sequence: Start pulse toggles RUN latch; Stop pulse/level forces stop.

    Status codes: statusCode INT → 0=Idle, 1=Running, 2=Fault

    Notes: Includes optional low/high PV “hold” with hysteresis (normal-stop class).
