 METHOD: _SetpointInputControl
 Purpose: Handle HMI writes for manual output using OSCAT TUNE2. Any external
          write to manualOutputPct bigger than the configured step will pulse
          SET for one scan. No SU/SD buttons here (PressureCtrl doesn’t use them).
 Objetivo: Tratar escrita da HMI no manualOutputPct via TUNE2. Mudança externa
           > passo gera pulso SET de 1 varredura. Sem botões ↑/↓ neste FB.
